  "keyFeatures": [
    "JUnit 5 extension system for managing external services",
    "52+ System-X service integrations (AWS, Azure, Kafka, databases, etc.)",
    "Support for local (TestContainers) and OpenShift deployments",
    "Integration testing for Apache Camel applications (Quarkus & Spring Boot)",
    "Flexible credential management (HashiCorp Vault, YAML files)",
    "JBang CLI tool for terminal usage",
    "Service abstraction with Account, Client, and Validation pattern"
